Bash configuration

Files:
    - bashrc
        * Uses bash completion and colored terms if available.
        * Has a long list of personal aliases
        * Linked to '~/.bashrc'
        * $PATH is set to ~/bin/ this folder contain
          symbolic links to executables.
    - git-completion.bash
        * Adds tab completion to git commands and arguments.
        * linked to '~/.git-completion.bash'
